      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project lovers and DIY mechanics! This vehicle is looking for a new home and some serious TLC to get back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a budget-friendly restoration project or a reliable source of parts. If you're ready to roll up your sleeves and bring this car back to life, it's waiting for you!",
